ve positioning contributed.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/121043904/image_121043904.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743842-allspring-high-yield-bond-fund-q3-2024-commentary", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 15:05:00"}, {"id": "4743430", "title": "Santa's Stunning Stocking Surprises: 5 High Yield Blue-Chip Bargains For 2025", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/158313365/image_158313365.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Santa giving Caucasian boy Christmas gift\" data-id=\"158313365\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1106px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/158313365/image_158313365.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/158313365/image_158313365.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/158313365/image_158313365.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/158313365/image_158313365.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/158313365/image_158313365.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/158313365/image_158313365.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/158313365/image_158313365.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/158313365/image_158313365.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Jose Luis Pelaez Inc/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><stron