age_1676709640.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1676709640/image_1676709640.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Based on the newly launched gold emissions curve, S&amp;P Global Commodity Insights found that 329 primary gold mines emitted greenhouse gases at an average rate of 792 kilograms of CO<sub>2</sub> equivalent per paid ounce of gold (kgCO</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1676709640/image_1676709640.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743833-green-investing-primary-gold-ghg-emissions-intensities-decline", "pub_date": "2024-12-12 14:50:00"}, {"id": "4743816", "title": "Phreesia Has Turned The Corner, Can It Continue To Mend?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501708932/image_501708932.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Surgeons adjusting lights in hospital operating theatre\" data-id=\"501708932\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501708932/image_501708932.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501708932/image_501708932.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501708932/image_501708932.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501708932/image_501708932.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/501708932/image_501708932.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s